<item>
            <title>[FELIX-5271] System bundle location incompatible with fileinstall</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5271</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Fileinstall accesses the system bundle by its location &quot;System Bundle&quot;. Connect uses the location &quot;felix-connect&quot; though. So fileinstall fails with a NPE. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think it would be better to change the location to &quot;System Bundle&quot; as this might happen with other bundles too. Additionally we could check if fileinstall could simply load the bundle 0 which I think should always work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
